replies.body:
Can an analysis of the Q+E hitbox/stun bug be prioritized with the width increase? Examples here: http://boards.na.leagueoflegends.com/en/c/bug-report/8UbfJEPt-gameplay-syndras-broken-stunkb-10-patches-and-counting

The reliability of the spell has been broken for a long time, regardless of the actual width hitbox. It straight up fails to do anything, or selectively only damages but applies no CC. It isn't a once in a blue moon bug, either - I consistently run into it at least 25-30% of the time in every match.

I've been trying to find a solution with RiotLoveStrut but there's only so much speculation and data grabbing I've been able to do ; _ ;
